Before make:

rm -r include
ln -s ../include ./
ln -s classify_cell.cc ./
ln -s globals.cc ./

after make, the script example 1: marker and refmesh are separate 

marker -g box.vog -r ref1.plan -tag refine1.dat -o ref2.plan
refmesh  -g box.vog -pr ref1.plan -r ref2.plan -o box2.vog -c2p c2pbox2.txt


script example 2: refine 

refine -g box.vog -r ref1.plan -tag refine1.dat -o box2.vog -oplan ref2.plan -c2p c2pbox2.txt
